snippet.title: Croc: Legend of the Gobbos gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Croc: Legend of the Gobbos, PC game produced by Fox Interactive in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/croc-legend-of-the-gobbos/1828/
Starting the adventure of this little crocodile, Croc: jumping the platform of first stage.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Adventures of Lomax - https://youtu.be/AAfzYjowuxU
Heart of Darkness - https://youtu.be/uw5ptES1yis
